trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:Accessibility.__MIDL_IWinTypes_0009" /> and all of its exposed members are part of a managed wrapper for the Component Object Model (COM) accessibility interface.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:Accessibility.__MIDL_IWinTypes_0009" /> 和其所有公開成員，是元件物件模型 (COM) 協助工具介面的 Managed 包裝函式的一部分。

trans-unit.source: For more information about <xref:Accessibility.__MIDL_IWinTypes_0009>, see the Microsoft Active Accessibility documentation in the MSDN library at http://msdn.microsoft.com/library.
trans-unit.target: 如需有關<xref:Accessibility.__MIDL_IWinTypes_0009>，請參閱 MSDN library 中的 Microsoft Active Accessibility 文件http://msdn.microsoft.com/library。
